Xchanges in the list of vertices).  If {\bf Y move} is selected, all
Xthree sets of axes are modified.  These operators work in screen space,
Xnot model space, so using them with an oblique view moves the model in
Xmore than one axis (Figure \ref{eo-xymove} for example)..
