XControl has again been passed to the {\bf OBJ EDIT} state. Notice that
Xall of the primitives are illuminated (Figure \ref{eo-cgrp}).
XAlthough only the parameters for the torus will be changed in the
Xdisplay, the ellipsoid in group ``b.g'' will be affected by the edit.
X
X\begin{figure}
X\centering \includegraphics{eo-cgrp321.ps}
X\caption{All Primitives Translated by (3, 2, 1).}
X\label{eo-cgrp321}
X\end{figure}
X
X\noindent
X{\tt
Xmged> {\em translate 3 2 1}\\
Xmged>\\
X}
X
XThe key point of the torus is moved to 3, 2, 1. All other primitives are
Xmoved by the same amount.  See Figure \ref{eo-cgrp321}.
X
X\noindent
X{\tt
Xmged> {\em press reject}\\
Xmged>\\
X}
X
XControl has now returned to the VIEWING state.
END-of-h.tex
